Force Shield 63 Wiz/Nec - HP Rune Shield + Mana Regen 
Blood of Thule Nec 61 - Poison DoT 
Legacy of Zek Nec 61 - Warrior Pet with New Model 
Rune of Death Nec 62 - Pet Haste & Stat Buff 
Saryn's Kiss Nec 62 - Magic Based DoT 
Embracing Darkness Nec 63 - Magic Based DoT + Snare 
Saryn's Companion Nec 63 - Rogue Pet with New Model 
